; Coverage for amount.cc
; Time colon display converts decimal fractions of hours to minutes.
; 1.50h becomes 1:30h (0.50 * 60 = 30 minutes).
; 2.75h becomes 2:45h (0.75 * 60 = 45 minutes).

2024/01/01 * Work morning
    (Billable:Client)    1.50h

2024/01/02 * Work afternoon
    (Billable:Client)    2.75h

test bal --time-colon
               4:15h  Billable:Client
end test
